title: Priestess Discography
description:
2005 - Hello Master
2009 - Prior to the Fire

Took forever to download these from a Russian tracker.
Properly repackaged, renamed, re-tagged, and sorted.

Sound quality on Hello Master is great EXCEPT for one thing.  It sounds like it is clipping on some parts.  A little popping and buzzing.  This is the best I can do, though.  I've long lost my original CD for this abum.

Sound quality on Prior to the Fire is EXCELLENT.

If you enjoy, please buy their merch and go to a show.
